rows.label: qev090702_MSG0001
rows.name: Finally back, are you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0002
rows.name:
I fully understand that you aren't finished yet,
but something's taken precedence. However...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0003
rows.name:
I'll be good enough to offer an extension
on our little contest in the meantime.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_JNK0010
rows.name: Brag

rows.label: qev090702_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell H.B. that you are already done.

rows.label: qev090702_JNK0020
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev090702_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask H.B. what this new issue is.

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0004
rows.name: Yes, I realize youâ€”what? Done? As in completed?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, naturally, I completed them as well,
so I suppose it's not impossible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0006
rows.name: Still this is something of a...shock.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0007
rows.name: It seems my initial assessment of you may have been lacking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0008
rows.name:
It's a matter of extreme import. But since those three jobs
were too much for you, this is...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0009
rows.name: Hold a moment. Wait...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0010
rows.name: This says you've completed them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0011
rows.name: Fascinating. You're almost as skilled and talented as I.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0012
rows.name:
Though I suppose that's generous,
given the gap in our completion times.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0013
rows.name:
Well, you appear more capable than
I first thought based on your...everything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0014
rows.name: Perhaps it would be best to brief you on this mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0015
rows.name:
One of our citizens was cornered by hostile indigens
in a cavern and attacked.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0016
rows.name: He is a scientist of most considerable repute.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0016_02
rows.name: New LA cannot afford to lose his talents.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0017
rows.name: Do you understand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0017_2
rows.name:
Even a moment's delay on our part
could risk the future of human technology.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0018
rows.name: Do you feel capable of assisting me in this operation?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0019
rows.name:
I'm certain someone of your proficiency
will only hold me back a little.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_JNK0030
rows.name: Accept

rows.label: qev090702_SEL0031
rows.name: Agree to help.

rows.label: qev090702_JNK0040
rows.name: Decline

rows.label: qev090702_SEL0041
rows.name: Tell H.B. to do it himself.

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0020
rows.name: Excellent. Let us set out immediately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0021
rows.name: Ah, a fool's pride. The downfall of many.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0022
rows.name:
Gain control of your petty feelings and come along.
We leave at once![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090702_MSG0023
rows.name:
I'm taking a risk on you, you know?
I hope you will not disappoint.[ST:wait ]
